\c 30
\s Rwiyo rwekuvonga
\d Pisarema, rwiyo pakutsaurira Dhavhidhi imba.
\p
\v 1 Ndichakukudzai, Jehovha, nokuti makandisimudza\x + Map. 107.32.\x*, uye hamuna kuita vavengi vangu vafare pamusoro pangu\x + Map. 35.19,24. Map. 13.4.\x*.
\v 2 Jehovha, Mwari wangu, ndakachema kwamuri\x + Map. 88.13.\x*, uye mukandirapa\x + Map. 6.2.\x*.
\v 3 Jehovha, makakwidza mweya wangu\x + Map. 86.13.\x* kubva paSheori\x + Map. 16.10.\x*; makandichengeta ndiri mupenyu kuti ndirege kuburukira kugomba\x + Map. 28.1.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Imbirai Jehovha nziyo dzekurumbidza, imwi vatsvene vake\x + Map. 50.5.\x*, muvonge pachirangariro cheutsvene hwake.
\v 5 Nokuti \add pane\add* chinguvana pakutsamwa kwake\x + Isa. 26.20.54.7,8. Map. 103.9.\x*; asi tsitsi dzake ndedzeupenyu hwese\x + Map. 63.3.\x*. Pamadekwani kuchema kunopedza usiku \add hwese\add*\x + 2 VaKori. 4.17.\x*, asi pamangwanani pane mufaro\x + Map. 5.3.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Ini ndakati pakubudirira kwangu\x + Job. 29.18.\x*: Handingatongozununguswi\x + Map. 10.6.\x*.
\v 7 Jehovha, netsitsi dzenyu makamisa gomo rangu nesimba; makavanza chiso chenyu; ini ndikatambudzika\x + Map. 104.29. Det. 31.17.\x*.
\v 8 Ndakachema kwamuri, Jehovha; uye ndakakumbira kuna Ishe\x + Map. 142.1.\x*.
\v 9 Mune rubatsiro rwei muropa rangu, pakuburukira kwangu kugomba? Guruva ringakurumbidzai here? Ringadudzira chokwadi chenyu here\x + Map. 6.5.\x*?
\v 10 Inzwai Jehovha, mundinzwirei tsitsi; Jehovha, ivai mubatsiri wangu\x + Map. 27.7.\x*.
\p
\v 11 Makashandura kuchema kwangu kukava kutamba\x + Jer. 31.4,13. Marir. 5.15. Map. 149.3. 150.4.\x*; makasunungura saga rangu, mukasunga chiuno changu nemufaro\x + 1 Madz. 20.31.\x*;
\v 12 kuti rukudzo rwangu rwukuimbirei nziyo dzekurumbidza, urege kunyarara. Jehovha Mwari wangu, ndichakuvongai nekusingaperi.